{"tid":2452644,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"唔止facebook IG, 原來啲外賣apps一樣會賣資料","createTime":"2021-03-19T03:15:57.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-19T10:27:49.000Z","uid":155674,"like":7,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"9170789d75dbcce1c5f91afe2288c4701a4f07b1","tid":2452644,"uid":155674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T03:15:57.000Z","msg":"唔計頭幾位facebook同IG嗰啲<br />\n連Ubereat同埋Deliveroo呢啲賣service嘅app都一樣會賣用戶資料俾人 <br />\ndown app之前真係要睇清楚<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n出賣私隱App排行Top50 IG比FB賣更多用戶資料 有個外賣App排第4<br />\n<br />\n由於App Store要求第三方App開發者揭露會收集用戶哪些個人數據。瑞士雲端存儲服務公司pCloud有見及此，就統計過App Store熱門App，發現有52%手機App竟會向第三方共享用戶的位置、聯絡人、財務資料、搜索歷史等等數據！Instagram與Tinder等等港人常用的App都有上榜！<br />\n<br />\nSource: <a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E6%95%B8%E7%A2%BC%E7%94%9F%E6%B4%BB/598336/%E5%87%BA%E8%B3%A3%E7%A7%81%E9%9A%B1app%E6%8E%92%E8%A1%8Ctop50-ig%E6%AF%94fb%E8%B3%A3%E6%9B%B4%E5%A4%9A%E7%94%A8%E6%88%B6%E8%B3%87%E6%96%99-%E6%9C%89%E5%80%8B%E5%A4%96%E8%B3%A3app%E6%8E%92%E7%AC%AC4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E6%2595%25B8%25E7%25A2%25BC%25E7%2594%259F%25E6%25B4%25BB%2F598336%2F%25E5%2587%25BA%25E8%25B3%25A3%25E7%25A7%2581%25E9%259A%25B1app%25E6%258E%2592%25E8%25A1%258Ctop50-ig%25E6%25AF%2594fb%25E8%25B3%25A3%25E6%259B%25B4%25E5%25A4%259A%25E7%2594%25A8%25E6%2588%25B6%25E8%25B3%2587%25E6%2596%2599-%25E6%259C%2589%25E5%2580%258B%25E5%25A4%2596%25E8%25B3%25A3app%25E6%258E%2592%25E7%25AC%25AC4&d=Ip59BN4yZo1XWf66eFhBSqQEQZ%2FBMmOowG797g%2FgSDo%3D&h=f60ed005\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E6%95%B8%E7%A2%BC%E7%94%9F%E6%B4%BB/598336/%E5%87%BA%E8%B3%A3%E7%A7%81%E9%9A%B1app%E6%8E%92%E8%A1%8Ctop50-ig%E6%AF%94fb%E8%B3%A3%E6%9B%B4%E5%A4%9A%E7%94%A8%E6%88%B6%E8%B3%87%E6%96%99-%E6%9C%89%E5%80%8B%E5%A4%96%E8%B3%A3app%E6%8E%92%E7%AC%AC4</a>"},{"pid":"c73424ad9c07ea5caea3f0fbdd52c0379267ef3a","tid":2452644,"uid":343551,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,